<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>How do digital media and the cinematic arts work together, make meaning, and effect change? <span class="title-main">Cinema &amp; Digital Media </span>is an interdisciplinary major that combines media theory, media history, and media-making to help students develop an understanding of creative and computational media technologies. Students get hands-on experience with independent and experimental approaches to digital cinema and other screen-based work.</p>
